{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"roleHeading":"Type Alias","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"typealias","externalID":"c:PWTypes.h@T@PushwooshRegistrationHandler","title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler"],"title":"Related Documentation"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typedef"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)","preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This closure is called when the device registration process finishes, either successfully or with an error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The handler receives two parameters:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"token"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The push token string if registration succeeded, or "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if it failed"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"error"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": An error object if registration failed, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if it succeeded"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle registration result with UI updates and backend sync:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func registerForNotifications() {","    let registrationHandler: PushwooshRegistrationHandler = { token, error in","        if let error = error {","            self.logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","            self.updateNotificationStatus(.failed)","            return","        }","","        guard let token = token else { return }","","        self.logger.info(\"Push token received: \\(token.prefix(20))...\")","        self.updateNotificationStatus(.registered)","","        self.syncPushTokenWithBackend(token)","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(withCompletion: registrationHandler)","}","","func syncPushTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","    let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","    apiClient.post(\"\/devices\/register\", body: [","        \"push_token\": token,","        \"hwid\": hwid,","        \"platform\": \"ios\"","    ])","}"]}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshErrorHandler":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\